{"tid":1720070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［警告CU］如中大校內情況惡化，警方將迫不得已介入！","createTime":"2019-11-14T08:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T09:00:27.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf84964808bb0b40b3289787256b0f3fac3df5b","tid":1720070,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:50:36.000Z","msg":"1636 警方記者會：正作風險評估，如中大校內情況惡化至對其他人造成危險，將逼不得已介入。警方不會透露行動細節和部署。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mt0FP6s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmt0FP6s.png&h=857d196d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e211092a70b1fb56a960c22cba89710d25aca861","tid":1720070,"uid":41974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:51:57.000Z","msg":"直升機空降，水路上岸，正面突入<br />\n<br />\n應該都係咁上下"},{"pid":"c5ff09ee382f7890bb84b40558ad55ab480b4254","tid":1720070,"uid":302917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"#安全威脅觀察 #氣象巴打隨筆 <br />\n<br />\n講白啲姐係滲透入中大，留意唔同小隊既組織，之後等時間上門拉。大家做野嗰陣需要提高警覺，唔好透露太多個人資訊。<br />\n<br />\n你既個人資訊唔限於自己嗰樣。"},{"pid":"c8a10b7816be49cb04017b44d78682711f83e236","tid":1720070,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:52:43.000Z","msg":"都戇撚鳩<br />\n中大生番中大關佢撚事"},{"pid":"230c958d962d9cda39eedbd1272bf74efd305fc9","tid":1720070,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:53:59.000Z","msg":"毅進仔以為自己可以管治大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec284196cbb821b4bce14adfb85540234bc4164","tid":1720070,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}